          "id": "63e8bc848f08b08d63d54729",
          "bodyHtml": "<p>The <strong>UN’s emergency relief coordinator Martin Griffiths</strong> has said “we have failed the people in north-west Syria” and they “rightly feel abandoned.”</p> <p>In a Twitter post he added:</p> <blockquote class=\"quoted\"> <p>Looking for international help that hasn’t arrived.<br>My duty and our obligation is to correct this failure as fast as we can.<br>That’s my focus now.”</p> </blockquote>  <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/UNReliefChief/status/1624701773557469184\">  <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">At the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/T%C3%BCrkiye?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Türkiye</a>-<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Syria?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Syria</a> border today.<br>We have so far failed the people in north-west Syria.<br>They rightly feel abandoned. Looking for international help that hasn’t arrived.<br>My duty and our obligation is to correct this failure as fast as we can.<br>That’s my focus now.</p>&mdash; Martin Griffiths (@UNReliefChief) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/UNReliefChief/status/1624701773557469184?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 12, 2023</a></blockquote>  </figure>  <p>On Saturday he spoke of the “devastating” scenes he had witnessed in Turkey as he visited the quake-hit areas.</p>  <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/UNReliefChief/status/1624475713653833728\">  <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">What I saw today in <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/T%C3%BCrkiye?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Türkiye</a> was devastating. <br><br>What were once homes, filled with families and memories, now lay contorted and tangled.<br><br>Our thoughts are with those affected and we will continue to support in any way we can. <a href=\"https://t.co/bhMDR1oEGN\">pic.twitter.com/bhMDR1oEGN</a></p>&mdash; Martin Griffiths (@UNReliefChief) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/UNReliefChief/status/1624475713653833728?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 11, 2023</a></blockquote>  </figure>",
